  (#122214) Create /var/lib/xkb so xorg-server doesn't fail later when trying
  to write to /usr/share/X11/xkb/compiled.

  07 Feb 2006; Donnie Berkholz <spyderous@gentoo.org>;
  xkeyboard-config-0.7.ebuild:
